  },
  {
    "surahId": 100,
    "ayahNumber": 6,
    "arabicText": "إِنَّ ٱلْإِنسَٰنَ لِرَبِّهِۦ لَكَنُودٌۭ",
    "translationText": "Indeed, the human being is ungrateful to his Lord."
  },
  {
    "surahId": 100,
    "ayahNumber": 7,
    "arabicText": "وَإِنَّهُۥ عَلَىٰ ذَٰلِكَ لَشَهِيدٌۭ",
    "translationText": "And he bears witness to that."
  },
  {
