    "translationText": "And he is fierce in his love of wealth."
  },
  {
    "surahId": 100,
    "ayahNumber": 9,
    "arabicText": "۞ أَفَلَا يَعْلَمُ إِذَا بُعْثِرَ مَا فِى ٱلْقُبُورِ",
    "translationText": "Does he not know? When the contents of the graves are scattered around."
