    "translationText": "And the contents of the hearts are obtained."
  },
  {
    "surahId": 100,
    "ayahNumber": 11,
    "arabicText": "إِنَّ رَبَّهُم بِهِمْ يَوْمَئِذٍۢ لَّخَبِيرٌۢ",
    "translationText": "Their Lord, on that Day, is fully informed of them."
  }
